trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigör alla resurser som används av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method is a simple call to <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden är ett enkelt anrop till <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Calling `Dispose` allows the resources used by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform> to be reallocated for other purposes.
trans-unit.target: Anropar `Dispose` tillåter resurserna som används av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>att fördelas för andra ändamål.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>

trans-unit.source: For more information about `Dispose`, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om `Dispose`, se [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigör alla resurser som används av den aktuella instansen av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>.
trans-unit.target: Anropa `Dispose` när du är klar med hjälp av <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den `Dispose` metoden lämnar kvar det <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>oanvändbar.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Efter att `Dispose`, måste du släppa alla referenser till den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>så skräpinsamlingen kan frigöra minne som den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>var upptar.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) och [implementera en metod för ta bort](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid anropet `Dispose` innan du släpper senaste referens till <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: De resurser som den använder frigörs annars inte förrän skräpinsamlingen anrop av <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>objektets `Finalize` metod.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Släpper de ohanterade resurser som används av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform"> </xref> och släpper du de hantera resurserna.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()` method and the `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden anropas av allmänheten `Dispose()` metod och `Finalize` metod.

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the disposing parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`anropar den skyddade `Dispose(Boolean)` metod med parametern disposing inställd på `true`.

trans-unit.source: `Finalize` invokes `Dispose` with disposing set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: `Finalize`anropar `Dispose` med avyttring inställd på `false`.

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform> references.
trans-unit.target: När den `disposing` parametern är `true`, den här metoden Frigör alla resurser som innehas av alla hanterade objekt som den här <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>referenser.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden startar den `Dispose()` metod för varje refererade till objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Frisläpp både hanterade och ohanterade resurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> att släppa endast resurser som inte hanteras.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Släpper de ohanterade resurser som används av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform"> </xref>.
